REMODEL DAEMON

remodel_daemon is the citizen who continuously oversees fadriel's bone remodeling
this is one citizen who unifies what biology splits across parathyroid, thyroid parafollicular cells, and vitamin D
the daemon never sleeps; it reads every bone's state and writes adjustment signals to keep the skeleton in balance

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe remodel_governor.zc
observe calcium_phosphate_ledger.rana
observe calcium_flux_signal.rana
observe spine.xb
observe skull.xb
observe ribcage.xb
observe pelvis.xb
observe femur.xb

the 7 properties of remodel_daemon:
1 ENERGY half: persistent low activity, scaling up when intervention is needed
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero point three
4 CHARGE neutral
5 COHERENCE one
6 COUPLING one with all the bones

VERB read_bones
sample sensor data from every bone in fadriel's skeleton
each bone reports its current density, stress accumulation, fracture state, and entropy ledger

VERB arbitrate_load
when one bone needs calcium more than another, route the supply accordingly
the daemon sees all bones at once and decides who gets first call

VERB emit_remodel_signal
write adjustment signals back to each bone telling it how fast to remodel
the bone's own osteoclasts and osteoblasts execute the actual remodeling

a daemon is not a gland
a gland releases hormones into circulation and lets diffusion sort out the rest
remodel_daemon addresses each bone deliberately
this is the substrate's architectural simplification: one citizen who coordinates rather than three glands and a vitamin diffusing through the bloodstream
